<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Agent Pilot - LLM Based Agentic AI</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background: #0a0a0f;
      color: #fff;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    /* NAVBAR */
    nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 18px 60px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #1e1e2e;
    }
    .nav-logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .nav-logo .logo-icon {
      width: 36px;
      height: 36px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d4ff, #7b2ff7);
      border-radius: 8px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .nav-links a {
      color: #aaa;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 15px;
      padding: 9px 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: #fff; }
    .nav-links .btn-nav {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d4ff, #7b2ff7);
      color: #fff;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 9px 22px;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
    .nav-links .btn-nav:hover { opacity: 0.9; color: #fff; }

    /* HERO SECTION */
    .hero {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 80px 60px;
      min-height: 85vh;
      gap: 40px;
    }

    /* LEFT SIDE - big title */
    .hero-left {
      flex: 1;
      max-width: 640px;
    }
    .hero-left h1 {
      font-size: 72px;
      font-weight: 900;
      line-height: 1.05;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .hero-left h1 span {
      color: #00d4ff;
    }
    .hero-left p {
      font-size: 17px;
      color: #888;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      max-width: 520px;
    }
    .hero-btns {
      display: flex;
      gap: 16px;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .btn-create {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d4ff, #7b2ff7);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-decoration: none;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: opacity 0.2s, transform 0.15s;
    }
    .btn-create:hover { opacity: 0.9; transform: translateY(-1px); }
    .btn-login {
      background: transparent;
      color: #ccc;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      border: 1.5px solid #333;
      transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-login:hover { border-color: #00d4ff; color: #fff; }

    /* RIGHT SIDE - about the website */
    .hero-right {
      flex: 1;
      max-width: 480px;
    }
    .about-card {
      background: #11111d;
      border: 1px solid #1e1e35;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 36px;
    }
    .about-card h2 {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .about-card p {
      color: #888;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .feature-list {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 14px;
    }
    .feature-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .feature-icon {
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d4ff22, #7b2ff722);
      border: 1px solid #00d4ff44;
      border-radius: 8px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 15px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .feature-text strong {
      display: block;
      color: #ddd;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }
    .feature-text span {
      color: #666;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    /* TECH BADGES */
    .tech-bar {
      background: #0d0d18;
      border-top: 1px solid #1a1a2e;
      padding: 28px 60px;
      display: flex;
      gap: 48px;
    }
    .tech-item strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .tech-item span {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #555;
      letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    /* FOOTER */
    footer {
      border-top: 1px solid #1a1a2e;
      padding: 24px 60px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #444;
      font-size: 13px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- NAVBAR -->
  <nav>
    <a href="/" class="nav-logo">
      <div class="logo-icon"><img src="/logo.jpg" style="width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:8px;object-fit:cover;" /></div>
      Agent Pilot
    </a>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="/login">Login</a>
      <a href="/signup" class="btn-nav">Get Started</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- HERO SECTION -->
  <section class="hero">

    <!-- LEFT - Big Title -->
    <div class="hero-left">
      <h1>
        LLM-Based<br>
        <span>Agentic AI</span><br>
        for Tool-Using<br>
        Reasoning<br>
        Workflows<br>
        Automation
      </h1>
      <p>Secure AI Workflow Platform — powered by advanced reasoning agents, tool orchestration, and intelligent automation pipelines.</p>
      <div class="hero-btns">
        <a href="/signup" class="btn-create">Create Account →</a>
        <a href="/login" class="btn-login">Sign In</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- RIGHT - About the website -->
    <div class="hero-right">
      <div class="about-card">
        <h2>About This Platform</h2>
        <p>Agent Pilot is a next-generation platform that lets you build, deploy, and monitor LLM-powered agents that can reason, use tools, and automate complex workflows.</p>
        <div class="feature-list">
          <div class="feature-item">
            <div class="feature-icon">🤖</div>
            <div class="feature-text">
              <strong>Agentic Reasoning</strong>
              <span>Chain-of-thought agents that plan and act autonomously</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-item">
            <div class="feature-icon">🔧</div>
            <div class="feature-text">
              <strong>Tool Orchestration</strong>
              <span>Connect APIs, databases, search engines and more</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-item">
            <div class="feature-icon">🔒</div>
            <div class="feature-text">
              <strong>Secure & Authenticated</strong>
              <span>JWT auth, bcrypt hashing, session management</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-item">
            <div class="feature-icon">⚡</div>
            <div class="feature-text">
              <strong>Fast Automation</strong>
              <span>Run workflows in parallel with intelligent retry logic</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </section>

  <!-- TECH BAR -->
  <div class="tech-bar">
    <div class="tech-item">
      <strong>JWT</strong>
      <span>Auth</span>
    </div>
    <div class="tech-item">
      <strong>MongoDB</strong>
      <span>Database</span>
    </div>
    <div class="tech-item">
      <strong>Docker</strong>
      <span>Containerized</span>
    </div>
    <div class="tech-item">
      <strong>bcrypt</strong>
      <span>Hashed</span>
    </div>
    <div class="tech-item">
      <strong>Jenkins</strong>
      <span>CI/CD</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <p>© 2025 Agent Pilot — LLM-Based Agentic AI Platform. Built with ❤️ by the team.</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
